# Track nothing by default — only the core files are re-included below.
# (Deny-by-default keeps data, build output, and scratch scripts out.)
*

# --- Core source files (repo root) ---
!.gitignore
!analysis.Rmd
!analysis.Rnw
!references.bib

# --- Proposal folder: keep folder reachable, ignore contents, ---
# --- then track only the exported proposal PDF (no data, no .docx). ---
!Proposal/
Proposal/*
!Proposal/proposal.pdf
